---
import "../styles/global.scss";
import "@fontsource/annie-use-your-telescope";
import "@fontsource/abel"
---

<div class=" section aboutMe" >
    <div class="aboutMe-main">
        <h1 class="aboutMe-title">About me</h1>
        <div class="container aboutMe-container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12" style="text-align: center;">
                    <img src="me.jpeg" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                    <h3 >Hey! Thanks for stopping by :)</h3>
                    <p >My name is Oscar, I majored as a mechatronics engineer at Tecnol√≥gico de Monterrey in 2021 and I currently have two years of experience working as a software engineer.</p>
                    <p>I started my fascination for coding while studying, working on school projects or messing with different libraries just for fun. </p>
                    <p>Today I consider myself as a well-rounded developer. I can help you create functional and pretty UIs, engineer that new API the company needs, or help you automate your service.</p>
                    <p>My mantra: The sky is the limit!</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .aboutMe {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-color: #ffff);
        color: var(--black-chocolate);
    }

    .aboutMe h3 {
        font-family: "Annie Use Your Telescope", "normal";
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .aboutMe p {
        font-family: "Abel", "normal";
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    .aboutMe img {
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    @media (min-width: 601px) and (max-width: 992px) { 
        .aboutMe img {
            max-width: 50%;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) { 
        .aboutMe img {
            max-width: 80%;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
        .aboutMe img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .aboutMe p {
        font-family: "Abel", "normal";
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    .aboutMe h3 {
        font-family: "Annie Use Your Telescope", "normal";
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        margin: 0.5rem;
    }

    .aboutMe-main {
        padding: 2rem ;
    }
    }

    .aboutMe-main {
        margin: 0 ;
    }

    .aboutMe-title {
        margin: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .aboutMe-container {
        max-width: fit-content;
    }
</style>
